&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behaviours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Broadcast Production Assistant will be expected to demonstrate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for developing and producing content for TV/Radio productions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to work effectively both individually and collaboratively as part of a production team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to think critically and creatively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working in an ethical and sustainable manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong work ethic and commitment in order to meet the standards required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognition of and compliance with equality and diversity in the workplace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Level&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This apprenticeship is set at level 3.&lt;/p&gt;
